SCHOOLS CELEBRATE A-LEVEL SUCCESS
----------------------------------------------------------------------

    Students in Richmond upon Thames school sixth forms are once again
    celebrating as they receive their A Level results.

    Results show that the 429 pupils in school sixth forms achieved A
    Level results above those seen nationally. The proportion of all
    entries graded as an A* to C was 85%, an increase of 7% points
    since last year. This compares with the national average of 77%.

